%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20To%20Walk%20Out%20Of%20Hospital%2C%206%20Days%20After%20He%20Was%20Stabbed%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20has%20been%20discharged%20from%20Mumbai's%20Lilavati%20Hospital%2C%20six%20days%20after%20he%20was%20seriously%20injured%20in%20a%20knife%20attack%20during%20a%20burglary%20attempt%20at%20his%20Bandra%20home.%20Currently%2C%20the%20discharge%20formalities%20are%20being%20carried%20out%20and%20actor%20is%20expected%20to%20walk%20out%20shortly.%20The%2054-year-old%20actor's%20mother%20and%20veteran%20actor%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20is%20with%20him.%20Mr%20Khan's%20wife%20and%20actor%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20was%20at%20the%20hospital%20but%20left%20for%20home%20a%20short%20while%20back.%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20been%20advised%20complete%20bed%20rest%20for%20a%20week%20and%20asked%20not%20to%20receive%20visitors%20to%20prevent%20any%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20force%20has%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20hospital%20as%20well%20as%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence%20as%20people%20have%20started%20gathering%20at%20both%20places%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20popular%20actor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20incident%20that%20shocked%20the%20nation%20and%20raised%20questions%20on%20Mumbai's%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20the%20actor%20suffered%20six%20stab%20injuries%20when%20a%20man%20who%20broke%20into%20his%20home%20attacked%20him%20with%20a%20knife.%20The%20actor%2C%20bleeding%20heavily%20from%20his%20wounds%2C%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20an%20auto-rickshaw%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20One%20of%20the%20injuries%20was%20on%20his%20spine%20and%20doctors%20said%20the%20knife%20missed%20his%20spinal%20cord%20by%20just%202%20mm.%20The%20spinal%20fluid%2C%20however%2C%20had%20leaked%20out%20and%20a%20surgery%20was%20conducted%20to%20fix%20this.%20The%20actor%20also%20underwent%20plastic%20surgery%20for%20injuries%20on%20his%20arm%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEliyama%20Philip%2C%20who%20looks%20for%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20sons%20Taimur%20and%20Jeh%2C%20has%20told%20police%20that%20she%20was%20the%20first%20to%20spot%20the%20intruder.%20She%20has%20said%20she%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20some%20noises%20around%202%20am.%20She%20saw%20the%20bathroom%20door%20ajar%20and%20the%20light%20on%20and%20assumed%20that%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20was%20checking%20on%20Jeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20then%20I%20went%20back%20to%20sleep%20but%2C%20again%2C%20I%20realised%20something%20was%20wrong.%20So%20I%20woke%20up%20again%20and%20saw%20a%20man%20come%20out%20of%20the%20bathroom%20and%20go%20into%20the%20boy's%20room.%20I%20quickly%20got%20up%20and%20went%20to%20Jeh's%20room.%20The%20attacker%20then%20put%20his%20finger%20near%20his%20mouth%20and%20said%20'Don't%20make%20any%20noise%2C%20nobody%20will%20go%20out'%20in%20Hindi%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Philip%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20rushed%20to%20pick%20up%20Jeh%2C%20the%20man%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20wooden%20stick%20and%20a%20long%20Hexa%20blade.%20ran%20towards%20me%20and%20tried%20attacking%20me.%20I%20tried%20to%20block%20the%20attack%20by%20putting%20my%20hand%20forward%2C%20but%20the%20blade%20hit%20me%20near%20the%20wrists%20of%20both%20my%20hands%20and%20on%20the%20middle%20finger%20of%20my%20left%20hand.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20'What%20do%20you%20want%3F'.%20He%20said%2C%20'I%20want%20money.'%20I%20asked%2C%20'How%20much%20do%20you%20want%3F'%20He%20said%20in%20English%2C%20'one%20crore'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Philip%20has%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20Ms%20Philip%20scream%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20rushed%20out%20of%20their%20room.%20When%20Mr%20Khan%20asked%20the%20intruder%20what%20he%20wanted%2C%20he%20attacked%20him%20with%20a%20wooden%20object%20and%20the%20hexa%20blade%2C%20Ms%20Philip%20said.%20%26quot%3BSaif%20Sir%20some