3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenviable%20perks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prestige%20that%20came%20along%20with%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20aimed%20to%20work%20with%20intelligent%20people%20to%20build%20technologies%20that%20could%20positively%20impact%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20excited%20about%20the%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20about%20cutting-edge%20technologies%20like%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20six%20years%20of%20tech%20consulting%20work%20and%20over%20three%20years%20at%20Harvard%20University%20as%20a%20techno-functional%20reporting%20analyst%2C%20Caperonis%20landed%20a%20full-time%20job%20as%20a%20business%20intelligence%20engineer%20at%20a%20top-tier%20tech%20company%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-pay-apple-nvidia-microsoft-alphabet-meta-amazon-tesla-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMagnificent%207%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20landing%20the%20job%20was%20far%20from%20easy%2C%20and%20the%20process%20was%20highly%20competitive.%20%26quot%3BI%20faced%20many%20rejections%20that%20allowed%20me%20to%20grow%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20it%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Caperonis%2C%20whose%20employment%20history%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a862c7f7-4917-4555-a721-368d0767dce7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDealing%20with%20rejection%20after%20rejection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disappointment%20began%20in%202012%20when%20Caperonis%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20at%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company.%20With%20two%20degrees%20and%20several%20years%20of%20relevant%20experience%2C%20she%20believed%20she%20was%20an%20overqualified%20candidate%20and%20a%20perfect%20fit%20for%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20answer%20technical%20questions%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20mind%20went