2466f4b3a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20thought%20she%20failed%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-before-big-tech-faang-interview-technical-questions-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20one%20top%20tech%20company%20lasted%20about%20eight%20hours%20and%20included%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20behavioral%20questions.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20she%20felt%20completely%20exhausted%20and%20feared%20she'd%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tides%20had%20turned.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20recruiter%20called%20me%20with%20the%20good%20news%2C%20I%20could%20hardly%20believe%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20so%20excited%20and%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20Caperonis%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20my%20life%20was%20about%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommends%20that%20anyone%20interested%20in%20Big%20Tech%20be%20very%20prepared%20to%20showcase%20their%20accomplishments%20and%20proficiency%20through%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20one%20she%20used%2C%20which%20she%20feels%20played%20a%20major%20part%20in%20landing%20the%20job%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1s7_xzgPJeo2kt4CdRye4nFug8dFif7yr%2Fpreview%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218231baf-0180-4a63-b70e-35dde3920d5a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20strong%20Big%20Tech%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3A%20Her%203%20tips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204079d43-25bd-4373-b622-7bd2efdfc430%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Create%20a%20gateway%20to%20your%20brand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-include-on-your-resume-2017