8f669dae09223df2bab63a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223233%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Hudson%2C%20CEO%20of%20Sanofi%2C%20said%20the%20pharmaceutical%20company%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20recommend%20which%20drugs%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20on%20development.%3Cp%3EJemal%20Countess%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Fortune%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESanofi's%20CEO%20said%20the%20pharma%20firm%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20decide%20to%20move%20a%20drug%20to%20the%20next%20developmental%20phase.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsobering%26quot%3B%20process%20because%20AI%20agents%20have%20no%20careers%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agent%20isn't%20wedded%20to%20the%20project%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Hudson%20said%20at%20Davos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Hudson%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20pharmaceutical%20firm%20Sanofi%2C%20has%20an%20argument%20for%20letting%20AI%20make%20top-level%20decisions%20in%20medicine%3A%20It%20has%20no%20attachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20panel%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-world-economic-forum-trump-inauguration-ai-day-one-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Hudson%20said%20Sanofi%20uses%20AI%20to%20recommend%20whether%20drugs%20should%20%26quot%3Bpass%20through%20a%20tollgate%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20essentially%20get%20approval%20to%20move%20to%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20Sanofi's%20senior%20decision-makers%20convene%20to%20discuss%20a%20drug%2C%20they%20start%20with%20an%20AI's%20recommendation%20for%20their%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20do%20that%20because%20it's%20very%20sobering%2C%20because%20the%20agent%20doesn't%20have%20a%20career%20at%20stake%2C%26quot%3B%20Hudson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20agent%20isn't%20wedded%20to%20the%20project%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20agent%20is%20dispassionately%20saying%3A%20'Don't%20go%20forward%20or%20go%20forward%20faster%2C%20or%20go%20forward%20and%20remember%20these%20things.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we're%20not%20used%20to%20having%20somebody%20without%20a%20career%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20room%20at%20a%20senior%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHudson%20also%20said%20that%20Sanofi%20typically%20takes%20about%2012%20to%2015%20years%20to%20fully%20develop%20a%20drug%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20market%20and%20that%20it's%20been%20practically%20using%20AI%20for%20about%20three%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20his%20estimate%2C%20that%20means%20AI%20has%20been%20around%20at%20Sanofi%20for%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiscovery%26quot%3B%20process%20for%20some%20drugs.%20That%20process%20is%20when%20manufacturers%20figure%20out%20what%20compounds%20should%20qualify%20as%20candidates%20for%20new%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pharmaceutical%20company%2C%20which%20makes%20drugs%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsulin-price-increased-last-decade-chart-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELantus%20insulin%20jabs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Plavix%20blood%20thinners%2C%20spends%20about%20three%20billion%20euros%2C%20or%20%243.1%20billion%2C%20on%20discovery%20within%20that%20timeframe%2C%20Hudson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20four%20other%20senior-level%20speakers%2C%20including%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%20and%20Aramco%20CEO%20Amin%20Nasser%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-predictions-how-ai-could-change-the-world-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20spoke%20positively%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20AI%20at%20the%20panel%2C%20saying%20people%20shouldn't%20be%20so%20worried%20that%20they%20might%20lose%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20jobs%20that%20are%20at%20risk%20are%20the%20jobs%20where%20the%20human%20isn't%20interested%20in%20AI.%20AI%20doesn't%20beat%20human%20plus%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Hudson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanofi's%20press%20team%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmaceutical-sanofi-ceo-paul-hudson-ai-drugs-career-at-stake-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737453722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678f673cae09223df2bab64c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmaceutical-sanofi-ceo-paul-hudson-ai-drugs-career-at-stake-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAnd%20we're%20not%20used%20to%20having%20somebody%20without%20a%20career%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20room%20at%20a%20senior%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hudson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmaceutical-sanofi-ceo-paul-hudson-ai-drugs-career-at-stake-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sparsh%20Shrivastava%20to%20join%20Naga%20in%20'NC24'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737453705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117425141%2Cimgsize-1210067.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Flaapataa-ladies-actor-to-join-naga-chaitanya-in-mystical-thriller-nc24-reports%2Farticleshow%2F117425113.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117425113.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENaga%20Chaitanya%20will%20star%20in%20the%20mystical%20thriller%20'NC24'%2C%20directed%20by%20Kar