ovation%20and%20be%20more%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d567934d-f552-4f4c-a398-4dfbd51f30df%5C%22%3E1.%20Clearer%20implementation%20of%20regulation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20last%20years%20the%20number%20of%20regulations%20and%20the%20length%20of%20the%20regulations%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20member%20country's%20market%20is%20different%2C%20but%20any%20time%20new%20legislation%20comes%20in%2C%20it%20can%20be%20implemented%20in%2027%20different%20ways%2C%20she%20said.%20To%20stop%20duplication%20and%20inefficiencies%2C%20the%20EU%20needs%20to%20create%20more%20alignment%20on%20implementation%20before%20signing%20laws%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219a3aa76-5933-4778-99cb-4e425a8cac3d%5C%22%3E2.%20Create%20a%20capital%20markets%20union%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20capital%20markets%20union%20(CMU)%20would%20create%20a%20single%20market%20for%20capital%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20that%20block%20cross-border%20investments%20and%20allowing%20nations%20to%20share%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20Europeans%20to%20invest%20in%20European%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20told%20BI.%20Creating%20a%20CMU%20would%20%26quot%3Bunlock%20billions%26quot%3B%20to%20create%20more%20of%20an%20innovation%20ecosystem.%20She%20wants%20to%20see%20the%20EU%20unbundle%20fees%20and%20allow%20pension%20funds%20to%20invest%20in%20equities%20with%20its%20biggest%20markets%2C%20like%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20you%20not%20make%20that%20transparent%20and%20lower%20the%20cost%3F%20Why%20do%20European%20mutual%20funds%20have%20to%20be%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20than%20American%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221219%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Profile%20of%20EY's%20managing%20partner%20EMEIA%20Julie%20Teigland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678e792fae09223df2baac4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Teigland%20is%20EY's%20managing%20partner%20for%20Europe%2C%20Middle%20East%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Africa%20(EMEIA)%3Cp%3EEY%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254a4e45b-6cfe-4bee-9067-69a8d58f7e42%5C%22%3E3.%20Support%20European%20champions%20by%20changing%20the%20laws%20on%20anti-competition%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20create%20any%20European%20champions%20in%20any%20industry%2C%20especially%20not%20in%20tech.%20Why%3F%20Because%20we%20don't%20allow%20them%20to%20combine%20across%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Teigland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeigland%20said%20the%20way%20to%20foster%20%26quot%3Bchampions%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20companies%20that%20help%20Europe%20compete%20with%20other%20economic%20powers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20find%20more%20balance%20between%20regulation%20that%20drives%20protectionism%20and%20ones%20that%20drive%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20on%20anti-competition%20need%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20particularly%20for%20larger%20companies%20in%20late-stage%20financing%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20all%20the%20things%20that%20have%20been%20knocked%20out%2C%20all%20the%20deals%20that%20have%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20table%20that%20Europe%20has%20said%20no%20way%2C%20we're%20protecting%20the%20individual%20consumers%20in%20the%20individual%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f0b042e-0169-4ac5-a1e7-40be9adb534a%5C%22%3E4.%20Stick%20together%20against%20Trump%20and%20China%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20the%20Chinese%20and%20America's%20strategy%20has%20been%20to%20pick%20the%20Europeans%20off%20one%20by%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Teigland%20said.%20But%20they%20have%20to%20work%20together%20to%20prevent%20this%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20just%20have%20to%20say%2C%20Donald%2C%20you're%20dealing%20with%20all%20of%20us.%20We're%20not%20going%20to%20take%20a%20deal%20for%20Germany%20and%20a%20deal%20for%20Spain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20can%20use%20Big%20Tech%20litigation%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-eu-trade-deficit-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20bargaining%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20offer%20to%20scale%20back%20its%20review%20of%20companies%20like%20Meta%2C%20Apple%2C%20and%20Google.%20They%20can%20also%20use%20the%20promise%20of%20more%20defense%20spending%20and%20purchasing%20US%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225bc030f-f9fd-4996-91e4-4f83fd23507b%5C%22%3E5.%20Create%20a%20clear%20investment%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20defense%20and%20industrial%20spending%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20Teigland%20thinks%20Europe%20needs%20a%20clearer%20investment%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Baligning%20on%20what%20we%20want%20at%20the%20beginning%2C%20instead%20of%20at%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20highlighted%20the%20defense%20and%20industrial%20spending%20plans%2C%20noting%20that%20even%20though%20Trump%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-divided-trump-call-boost-defense-spending-gdp-russia-ukraine-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpected%20to%20increase%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20defense%20industry%2C%20there%20had%20not%20been%20a%20mapping%20for%20industrial%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20recent%20conversation%20with%20a%20NATO%20General%2C%20Teigland%20highlighted%20issues%20with%20communications%20technology%20in%20tanks.%20The%20person%20shooting%20the%20mortars%20has%20%26quot%3Bto%20open%20the%20lid%2C%20use%20their%20Apple%20phone%20to%20dial%2C%20to%20call%20the%20guy%20to%20give%20him%20the%20coordinates%20because%20nothing%20links%20with%20each%20other%20across%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeigland%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20EU%20needs%20a%20map%20of%20who%20is%20producing%20what%20and%20how%20it%20combines%20so%20that%20it%20can%20determine%20where%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d0fda3b-a98f-4025-a91d-89fbf88c27e9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEurope's%20outlook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20going%20to%20take%20money%20to%20create%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20success%2C%20and%20combining%20forces%20is%20no%20small%20thing%20for%20the%20bureaucracy-heavy%20EU%20bloc.%20But%20Teigland%20said%20she's%20positive%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20groups%20are%20aligned%20about%20the%20need%20to%20boost%20competitiveness%20and%20trim%20down%20regulatory%20burdens%2C%20and%20senior%20EU%20politicians%20Teigland%20speaks%20to%20are%20%26quot%3Breally%20listening%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f5a3e957ed0ee001e25e7c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22709%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUrsula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20began%20her%20second%20mandate%20as%20President%20of%20the%20EU%20Commission%20in%20December%202024.%3Cp%3EThierry%20Monasse%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20moves%20by%20Ursula%20Von%20der%20Leyen%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20are%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20signs%20things%20that%20Europe%20is%20getting%20serious%20about%20boosting%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20a%20new%20mandate%20in%202024%20to%20lead%20the%20European%20Commission%20for%20another%20five%20years%2C%20Von%20der%20Leyen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F11%2F08%2Fthe-budapest-declaration%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20wants%20to%20launch%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimplification%20revolution%26quot%3B%20and%20cut%20regulatory%20%26quot%3B