%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20of%20failing%20to%20stop%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20drug%20trafficking%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20thinking%20in%20terms%20of%2025%20per%20cent%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20because%20they're%20allowing%20vast%20numbers%20of%20people%20--%20Canada's%20a%20very%20bad%20abuser%20also%20--%20vast%20numbers%20of%20people%20to%20come%20in%2C%20and%20fentanyl%20to%20come%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20thinking%20of%20enacting%20the%20tariffs%20on%20February%201.%20The%20New%20President%20also%20signed%20an%20order%20Monday%20directing%20agencies%20to%20study%20a%20host%20of%20trade%20issues%20including%20deficits%2C%20unfair%20practices%20and%20currency%20manipulation.%20These%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20further%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%2C%20Trump%20had%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20begin%20the%20overhaul%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%20trade%20system%20%26quot%3Bto%20protect%20American%20workers%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20taxing%20our%20citizens%20to%20enrich%20other%20countries%2C%20we%20will%20tariff%20and%20tax%20foreign%20countries%20to%20enrich%20our%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20inaugural%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexico%20was%20the%20largest%20trading%20partner%20of%20the%20US%20in%202023%20with%20a%20total%20two-way%20goods%20trade%20of%20%24807bn%2C%20an%20amount%20that%20surpassed%20US%20trade%20with%20China%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20state%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEU%20Imbalance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%2C%20Trump%20took%20aim%20at%20trade%20imbalances%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20too%2C%20saying%20it%20did%20not%20import%20enough%20American%20products.%20He%20added%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bstraighten%20that%20out%26quot%3B%20by%20using%20tariffs%20or%20by%20urging%20more%20oil%20and%20gas%20purchases%20from%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EU's%20economy%20commissioner%20said%20earlier%20Monday%20that%20it%20stood%20ready%20to%20defend%20its%20interests%2C%20while%20Canadian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20said%20Ottawa%20would%20work%20to%20ensure%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20US%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20inaugural%20address%2C%20Trump%20reiterated%20his%20plan%20also%20to%20set%20up%20an%20%26quot%3BExternal%20Revenue%20Service%26quot%3B%20to%20collect%20tariffs%2C%20duties%20and%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETikTok%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20ordered%20a%2075-day%20pause%20on%20enforcing%20a%20law%20that%20would%20effectively%20ban%20TikTok.%20His%20action%20delayed%20the%20implementation%20of%20an%20act%20that%20came%20into%20effect%20this%20week%2C%20prohibiting%20the%20distribution%20and%20updating%20of%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20the%20app's%20Chinese%20parent%20company%20must%20agree%20to%20sell%20a%20fifty%20per%20cent%20share%20to%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaving%20WHO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20also%20signed%20an%20order%20for%20the%20United%20States%20to%20exit%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20insisting%20Washington%20was%20unfairly%20paying%20more%20than%20China%20into%20the%20UN%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20order%2C%20the%20US%20was%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20organisation%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bmishandling%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20that%20arose%20out%20of%20Wuhan%2C%20China%2C%20and%20other%20global%20health%20crises%2C%20its%20failure%20to%20adopt%20urgently%20needed%20reforms%2C%20and%20its%20inability%20to%20demonstrate%20independence%20from%20the%20inappropriate%20political%20influence%20of%20WHO%20member%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20the%20largest%20funder%20of%20the%20Geneva-headquartered%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20President%20Trump%20also%20paused%20the%20disbursement%20of%20US%20foreign%20development%20assistance%20for%2090%20days.%20The%20move%20left%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20aid%20in%20limbo%2C%20dependent%20on%20a%20decision%20by%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20who%20was%20confirmed%20as%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20as%20the%20first%20cabinet%20member%20of%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaves%20Paris%20Climate%20Accord%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20immediately%20withdrew%20the%20United%20States%20from%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Accord%2C%20repeating%20an%20action%20he%20took%20during%20his%20first%20term.%20The%20order%20extends%20Trump's%20defiant%20rejection%20of%20global%20efforts%20to%20combat%20planetary%20warming%20as%20catastrophic%20weather%20events%20intensify%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20take%20a%20year%20to%20leave%20the%20agreement%20after%20submitting%20a%20formal%20notice%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20framework%20that%20underpins%20global%20climate%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVows%20To%20Take%20Panama%20Canal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20inaugural%20speech%2C%20Trump%20repeated%20his%20complaint%20that%20China%20was%20effectively%20%26quot%3Boperating%26quot%3B%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20through%20its%20growing%20presence%20around%20the%20vital%20waterway%2C%20which%20the%20United%20States%20handed%20over%20at%20the%20end%20of%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20give%20it%20to%20China%2C%20we%20gave%20it%20to%20Panama.%20And%20we're%20taking%20it%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20inside%20the%20US%20Capitol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20raising%20pressure%20for%20weeks%20over%20the%20canal%20--%20through%20which%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20US%20container%20traffic%20travels%20--%20and%20has%20repeatedly%20refused%20to%20rule%20out%20military%20force%20against%20Panama%2C%20historically%20friendly%20to%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Bank%20Settler%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20revoked%20sanctions%20against%20violent%20Israeli%20settlers%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20accused%20of%20abuses%20against%20Palestinians%2C%20undoing%20an%20unprecedented%20action%20taken%20by%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration.%20The%20move%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20concession%20to%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20amid%20a%20crucial%20ceasefire%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20a%20reporter%20whether%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20would%20maintain%20the%20truce%20and%20move%20on%20in%20the%20agreement%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20our%20war%3B%20it's%20their%20war.%20But%20I'm%20not%20confident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20he%20believed%20Hamas%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bweakened%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20war%20that%20began%20with%20its%20unprecedented%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20on%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BI%20looked%20at%20a%20picture%20of%20Gaza.%20Gaza%20is%20like%20a%20massive%20demolition%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20tycoon%20turned%20populist%20politician%20said%20that%20Gaza%20could%20see%20a%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%26quot%3B%20reconstruction%20if%20the%20plan%20moves%20ahead.%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20phenomenal%20location%20on%20the%20sea%20--%20best%20weather.%20You%20know%2C%20everything's%20good.%20It's%20like%2C%20some%20beautiful%20things%20could%20be%20done%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECuba%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReversing%20another%20one%20of%20Biden's%20more%20recent%20moves%2C%20Trump%20removed%20Cuba%20from%20a%20blacklist%20of%20state%20sponsors%20of%20t