agement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fiphone-17-air-what-we-know-so-far-about-apple-s-new-sleek-iphone-model-125012100540_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20vs%20BJP%20Over%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20'Raavan%20Came%20As%20Golden%20Deer'%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20two%20weeks%20left%20for%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election%2C%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20are%20stepping%20up%20attacks%20on%20each%20other.%20The%20two%20parties%20have%20now%20sparred%20over%20a%20remark%20by%20AAP%20convener%20and%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Raavan%2C%20the%20antagonist%20in%20Ramayana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20election%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20narrated%20the%20episode%20during%20which%20Raavan%20abducted%20Sita.%20%26quot%3BRamchandra%20ji%20went%20into%20the%20woods%20to%20arrange%20food%20after%20asking%20(brother)%20Laxman%20to%20look%20after%20Sita.%20Then%2C%20Raavan%20came%20in%20the%20disguise%20of%20a%20golden%20deer.%20Sita%20told%20Laxman%20that%20she%20wanted%20the%20deer.%20Laxman%20initially%20refused%20but%20then%20went%20in%20search%20of%20the%20deer.%20Raavan%20then%20changed%20his%20form%20(to%20a%20hermit)%20and%20managed%20to%20abduct%20Sita.%20These%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20like%20that%20golden%20deer.%20Don't%20fall%20in%20their%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ramayana%2C%20a%20demon-ascetic%20named%20Maricha%20was%20tasked%20with%20Raavan%20to%20lure%20Ram%20away%20from%20Sita.%20Maricha%20changed%20into%20a%20golden%20deer%20and%20Sita%20was%20so%20enamoured%20that%20she%20asked%20Ram%20to%20get%20it%20for%20her.%20Ram%20chased%20the%20deer%20into%20the%20woods%20and%20when%20he%20struck%20it%2C%20Mareech%20cried.%20Sita%20thought%20Ram%20had%20been%20injured%20and%20sent%20Laxman%20to%20look%20for%20him.%2