It%20is%20important%20to%20be%20alert%20because%20their%20real%20agenda%20is%20to%20capture%20power.%20Beware%20of%20their%20false%20dramas%20and%20take%20the%20correct%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sisodia%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20later%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20camping%20outside%20my%20home%20because%20I%20insulted%20Raavan.%20They%20love%20Raavan%20so%20much.%20They%20have%20demonic%20tendencies.%20I%20want%20to%20warn%20the%20poor%20in%20Delhi%2C%20if%20these%20people%20come%2C%20they%20will%20swallow%20you%20like%20demons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737442440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F4fma68bg_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_21_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-arvind-kejriwal-aap-vs-bjp-over-arvind-kejriwals-raavan-came-as-golden-deer-remark-7523099%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20just%20two%20weeks%20left%20for%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election%2C%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20are%20stepping%20up%20attacks%20on%20each%20other.%20The%20two%20parties%20have%20now%20sparred%20over%20a%20remark%20by%20AAP%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Raavan%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-arvind-kejriwal-aap-vs-bjp-over-arvind-kejriwals-raavan-came-as-golden-deer-remark-7523099%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20balls%20on%20Sydney%20beaches%20found%20to%20contain%20toxic%20material%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737442353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F250b%2Flive%2F80aed990-d7c0-11ef-94fe-11958094d89a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcpql7wdz5vyo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20