%20of%20the%20police%20authority%20of%20Tala%20PS%20as%20well%20as%20the%20administrative%20wing%20of%20R.G%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20will%20not%20stand%20as%20a%20stumbling%20block%20on%20the%20way%20of%20trial%20of%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20he%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20prosecution%20correctly%20discharged%20the%20burden%20and%20placed%20sufficient%20evidence%20to%20establish%20the%20guilt%20of%20this%20accused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20defence%20could%20not%20establish%20the%20presence%20of%20any%20other%20person%20other%20than%20Roy%20and%20the%20victim%20in%20the%20seminar%20room%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20got%20the%20scope%20to%20explain%20the%20circumstances%20but%20he%20failed%20to%20offer%20any%20alternative%20explanation%20denying%20his%20presence%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20crime.%20He%20was%20unable%20to%20negate%20the%20contention%20that%20no%20one%20else%20could%20have%20inflicted%20the%20said%20injuries%20over%20the%20person%20of%20the%20deceased%20(victim).%20The%20bald%20plea%20of%20denial%20offered%20by%20the%20accused%20and%20his%20explanation%20made%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20examination%20U%2Fs%20351%20BNSS%2C%20do%20not%20lead%20me%20to%20hold%20that%20the%20accused%20could%20place%20any%20satisfactory%20explanation%20for%20which%20any%20suspicion%20can%20arise%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fao239mt_sanjay_625x300_18_January_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Was%20The%20Motive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20notes%20that%20Roy%20had%20said%20he%20was%20drunk%20when%20he%20entered%20the%20hospital%20premises.%20The%20court%20said%20there%20was%20no%20hostility%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20Roy%20and%20he%20attacked%20her%20%26quot%3Bon%20sudden%20impulse%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bmeet%20his%20lust%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20victim%20was%20obviously%20not%20his%20target%20or%20that%20it%20was%20not%20known%20to%20him%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20there%20in%20the%20said%20Seminar%20Room%20and%20the%20offence%20committed%20by%20him%20was%20not%20pre-planned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20precedents%20in%20law%2C%20the%20court%20said%20many%20murders%20have%20been%20committed%20without%20any%20known%20or%20prominent%20motive.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20motive%20is%20a%20psychological%20phenomenon.%20Mere%20fact%20that%20prosecution%20failed%20to%20translate%20that%20mental%20disposition%20of%20the%20accused%20into%20evidence%2C%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20no%20such%20mental%20condition%20existed%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20assailant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20proof%20can%20be%20expected%20in%20all%20cases%20as%20to%20how%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20accused%20worked%20in%20a%20particular%20situation%20but%20the%20same%20by%20itself%20is%20insufficient%20to%20lead%20to%20any%20inference%20adverse%20to%20the%20prosecution...%20I%20hold%20that%20the%20prosecution%20case%20will%20not%20face%20the%20failure%20for%20want%20of%20direct%20evidence%20about%20the%20motive%20of%20the%20convict%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2ahojl3o_kolkata-doctor-rapemurder-case_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Not%20Death%20Penalty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20notes%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20crime%20is%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20heinous%2C%20characterized%20by%20its%20brutality%20and%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20victim%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20judicial%20system%20has%20a%20stringent%20criteria%20for%20imposing%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20reserving%20it%20for%20cases%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bexceptionally%20heinous%20and%20shock%20the%20collective%20conscience%20of%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20considering%20the%20imposition%20of%20capital%20punishment%2C%20courts%20must%20grapple%20with%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20legal%2C%20moral%20and%20societal%20considerations.%20The%20principle%20of%20proportionality%20is%20paramount%20-%20the%20punishment%20must%20fit%20the%20crime.%20In%20cases%20of%20extreme%20brutality%20and%20cruelty%2C%20where%20the%20offence%20shocks%20the%20conscience%20of%20society%2C%20the%C2%A0argument%20for%20the%20ultimate%20punishment%20gains%20strength.%20However%2C%20this%20must%20be%20balanced%20against%20the%20principles%20of%20reformative%20justice%20and%20the%20sanctity%20of%20human%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20reformation%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20is%20another%20crucial%20factor%20that%20courts%20must%20consider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20judicial%20system%20must%20weigh%20whether%20the%20convict%2C%20given%20the%20nature%20and%20circumstances%20of%20their%20crime%2C%20shows%20any%20potential%20for%20rehabilitation%20and%20reintegration%20into%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cited%20the%20Bachan%20Singh%20vs%20State%20of%20Punjab%20judgment%20in%201980%20which%20held%20that%20%26quot%3Blife%20imprisonment%20is%20the%20rule%20and%20death%20sentence%20an%20exception%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judiciary's%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20uphold%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20ensure%20justice%20based%20on%20evidence%2C%20not%20public%20sentiment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says%2C%20noting%20that%20there%20is%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20prior%20criminal%20behaviour%20by%20the%20convict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20realm%20of%20modern%20justice%2C%20we%20must%20rise%20above%20the%20primitive%20instinct%20of%20'an%20eye%20for%20an%20eye'%20or%20'a%20tooth%20for%20a%20tooth'%20or%20'nail%20for%20a%20nail'%20or%20'a%20life%20for%20a%20life'.%20Our%20duty%20is%20not%20to%20match%20brutality%20with%20brutality%2C%20but%20to%20elevate%20humanity%20through%20wisdom%2C%20compassion%20and%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20justice.%20The%20measure%20of%20a%20civilized%20lies%20not%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20exact%20revenge%2C%20but%20in%20its%20capacity%20to%20reform%2C%20rehabilitate%C2%A0and%20ultimately%20to%20heal%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20case%20does%20not%20meet%20the%20'rarest%20of%20the%20rare'%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20must%20resist%20the%20temptation%20to%20bow%20to%20public%20pressure%20or%20emotional%20appeals%20and%20instead%20focus%20on%20delivering%20a%20verdict%20that%20upholds%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20legal%20system%20and%20serves%20the%20broader%20interests%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737432000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F81haeca_sanjay-roy_625x300_21_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-rape-and-murder-case-sanjoy-roy-must-rise-above-eye-for-an-eye-why-no-death-penalty-for-rg-kar-convict-7522014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kolkata%20court%2C%20which%20sentenced%20RG%20Kar%20rape-murder%20case%20convict%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20has%20made%20stro