ure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20cannot%20reach%20a%20district%20hospital.%20So%2C%20Dr%20Taru%20emphasises%2C%20we%20need%20skilled%20healthcare%20on%20the%20peripheries.%20She%20believes%20the%20government%20must%20mandate%20and%20enforce%20the%20bond%20requiring%20medical%20graduates%20to%20be%20posted%20in%20rural%20areas%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20should%20apply%20to%20everyone%20including%20nurses%2C%20doctors%2C%20Ayurvedic%20practitioners%2C%20and%20Homoeopathic%20doctors.%E2%80%9D%20The%20project%2C%20she%20says%2C%20should%20be%20spotlighted%20as%20heroic%2C%20which%20will%20boost%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365338%2Fnagaland-institute-medical-sciences-research-nimsr-kohima-nagaland-dr-soumya-chakraborty-northeast-colleges%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emorale%20among%20medical%20students%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOptimal%20use%20of%20funds%20and%20ensuring%20accountability%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20used%20to%20think%20our%20rural%20hospitals%20suffered%20from%20lack%20of%20funds%2C%20and%20corruption%20led%20to%20further%20dilution%20of%20the%20available%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Taru%20shares.%20So%2C%20she%20was%20shocked%20when%20she%20learnt%20that%20every%20year%20Bihar%20sends%20back%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20PIP%20(Project%20Implementation%20Plan)%20%E2%80%94%20yearly%20funds%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20implement%20health%20schemes%20%E2%80%94%20funds%20unutilised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202017%2C%20Motihari%20had%20used%20only%2012%20percent%20of%20the%20funds%20sanctioned%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20learnt.%20The%20fallacy%20was%20rooted%20in%20an%20antiquated%20mindset.%20%E2%80%9CCorruption%20fear%20meant%20health%20officials%20were%20extremely%20reluctant%20to%20sanction%20money%20for%20anything.%20There%20was%20a