%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20instrument%2C%20once%20a%20symbol%20of%20celebration%2C%20became%20a%20marker%20of%20social%20exclusion%20and%20systemic%20oppression%2C%20which%20the%20artists%20were%20not%20fond%20of.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20revolutionary%20protest%2C%20changing%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20parai%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiberation%20from%20the%20chains%20of%20caste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inherent%20inequality%20fueled%20the%20rise%20of%20%E2%80%98Parai%20Marrupu%20Porattam%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20significant%20anti-caste%20movement%20led%20by%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20Federation.%20Originating%20in%20Cuddalore%20district%2C%20it%20spread%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%E2%80%9CMarrupu%E2%80%9D%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%9Cto%20deny%2C%E2%80%9D%20symbolising%20the%20movement%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20break%20free%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20caste-based%20occupations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20movement%2C%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20broader%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Izhi%20Thozhil%20Ethirppu%20Porattam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Refusal%20of%20Caste-Based%20Occupations)%20that%20spanned%20from%20the%20mid-1940s%20to%20the%201980s%2C%20witnessed%20the%20mass%20destruction%20of%20parai%20as%20a%20symbolic%20act%20of%20defiance.%20It%20gained%20significant%20momentum%20in%20northern%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20influenced%20similar%20movements%20in%20Eelam%20(Sri%20Lanka).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20key%20objective%20of%20the%20movement%20was%20to%20liberate%20future%20generations%20from%20the%20constraints%20of%20caste-based%20occupations%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manimaran.%20This%20principle%20was%20demonstrated%20at%20the%20Kathaaiyee%20Amman%20temple%20festival%20in%20Cuddalore.%20When%20local%20parai%20artists%20refused%20to%20participate%2C%20defying%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20the%20movement%2C%20artists%20from%20outside%20the%20region%20were%20brought%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Reddiyur%20Pandian%20on%20August%2015%2C%201987.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20many%2C%20including%20Manimaran%2C%20who%20understood%20the%20difference%20between%20picking%20an%20art%20form%20out%20of%20choice%20and%20picking%20it%20because%20that%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20he%20should%20do.%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20from%20the%20upper%20class%20came%20forward%20to%20play%20parai%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20because%20parai%E2%80%99s%20art%20status%20was%20not%20satisfactory%20for%20this%20hierarchical%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20Manimaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManimaran%2C%20and%20several%20others%20like%20him%2C%20are%20focusing%20on%20the%20correct%20usage%20of%20parai%20%E2%80%94%20an%20instrument%20of%20social%20change%20and%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20caste%20barrier%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20parai%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20dignity%20and%20earned%20a%20better%20platform%20to%20contribute%20to%20societal%20causes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20parai%20to%20educate%20people%20and%20create%20awareness%20on%20pressing%20societal%20issues%2C%20training%20them%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manimaran%2C%20who%20founded%20%E2%80%98Buddhar%20Kalai%20Kuzhu%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20academy%20teaching%20parai%20for%20all%20%E2%80%94%20since%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChange%20has%20to%20come%20within